title: Julie Bushby praises Sheridan Smith in The Moorside and tells viewers the show is ‘very close to the truth’ after some questioned authenticity
text:
TV Magazine IT'S ALL FACT Julie Bushby praises Sheridan Smith in The Moorside and tells viewers the show is ‘very close to the truth’ after some questioned authenticity 
The BBC show about Shannon Matthews showed details never before seen by the public but Julie says it’s all the truth BY ELLIE HENMAN, SHOWBIZ REPORTER 8th February 2017, 7:00 am
